{"title_page": "List of rivers of Louisiana", "text_new": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article of rivers of Louisiana, U.S.}}\n{{More footnotes|date=November 2019}}\n'''List of [[river]]s of [[Louisiana]]''' ([[U.S. state]]).\n\n==By [[drainage basin]]==\nThis list is arranged by drainage basin, with respective tributaries indented under each larger stream's name.\n\n===Gulf of Mexico===\n\n====East of the Mississippi====\n*[[Pearl River (Mississippi\u2013Louisiana)|Pearl River]]\n**[[Bogue Chitto River]]\n*''[[The Rigolets]]''\n**''[[Lake St. Catherine (Louisiana)|Lake St. Catherine]]''\n***''[[Lake Pontchartrain]]''\n****[[Lacombe Bayou]]\n****[[Tchefuncte River]]\n*****[[Bogue Falaya]]\n******[[Abita River]]\n****[[Tangipahoa River]]\n*****[[Sims Creek]]\n****[[Pass Manchac]]\n*****''[[Lake Maurepas]]''\n******[[Tickfaw River]]\n*******[[Natalbany River]]\n********[[Ponchatoula Creek]]\n*******[[Blood River (Louisiana)|Blood River]]\n******[[Amite River]]\n*******[[Bayou Manchac]]\n*******[[Comite River]]\n******[[Blind River (Louisiana)|Blind River]]\n*******[[Petite Amite River]]\n********[[New River (Louisiana)|New River]]\n*[[Bayou Bienvenue]]\n\n====Mississippi River====\n*[[Mississippi River]]\n\n=====Distributaries=====\n*[[Bayou Lafourche]]\n*[[Atchafalaya River]]\n**[[Bayou Cocodrie]]\n**[[Bayou Teche]]\n***[[Bayou Boeuf]]\n**[[Bayou Long]]\n***[[Belle River (Louisiana)|Belle River]]\n****[[Big Goddel Bayou]]\n*****[[Bay Natchez]]\n******[[Chopin Chute]]\n*******[[Lower Grand River]]\n********[[Upper Grand River]]\n********[[Bayou Plaquemine (Grand River tributary)|Bayou Plaquemine]]\n**[[Rouge Bayou]]\n***[[Bayou Jack]]\n**[[Bayou des Glaises]]\n\n=====Tributaries=====\n*[[Bayou Pierre]]<ref>{{Google maps|url=https://goo.gl/maps/FpLDMgfs45ZU4fnh7 |title=Bayou Pierre |access-date=January 5, 2020}}</ref>\n*[[Coles Creek (Mississippi)|Coles Creek]]<ref>{{Google maps|url=https://goo.gl/maps/7tnCPYWyQty6yvvT8 |title=Coles Creek |access-date=December 2