com.tn.gov.in/organisation.htm |title=Most Enterprises in India |publisher=Indcom.tn.gov.in |year=2011 |accessdate=10 September 2012 |ref={{sfnRef|Tamil Nadu enterprises|2011}}}}\n* {{cite web |url=http://www.tn.gov.in/deptst/agriculture.pdf |title=Tamil Nadu&nbsp;\u2013 States and Union Territories&nbsp;\u2013 Know India: National Portal of India |publisher=India.gov.in |date=31 March 2009 |accessdate=4 November 2010 |ref={{sfnRef|Tamil Nadu agricultural department|2009}}}}\n* {{cite web |url=http://nhm.nic.in/ActionPlan/ActionPlan_TamilNadu.pdf |title=National Horticulture Mission -Action Plan for Tamil Nadu |accessdate=10 September 2012 |year=2008 |ref={{sfnRef|Tamil Nadu horticulture|2008}} |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120227095454/http://nhm.nic.in/ActionPlan/ActionPlan_TamilNadu.pdf |archivedate=27 February 2012  }}\n* {{cite web |url=http://www.rubberboard.org.in/RSN/RSNEWSOCT06.pdf |title=Rubber Statistical News |year=2006 |accessdate=10 September 2012 |ref={{sfnRef|Rubber board|2006}} |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120717050628/http://www.rubberboard.org.in/RSN/RSNEWSOCT06.pdf |archive-date=17 July 2012 |url-status=dead  }}\n* {{cite web |url=http://www.teauction.com/statistics/indprodstate.asp |title=Production of Tea in India During And Up to August 2002 |publisher=Teauction.com |year=2002 |accessdate=10 September 2012 |ref={{sfnRef|Tea production in India|2002}}}}\n* {{cite web |url=http://assets.wwfindia.org/downloads/palm_oil_study_in_india___a_report.pdf |title=Oil Palm Sector in India&nbsp;\u2013 World Wildlife Fund&nbsp;\u2013 India |year=2004 |accessdate=10 September 2012 |ref={{sfnRef|Palmoil Study|2004}}}}\n* {{cite web |url=http://www.mssrf.org/ |title=M. S. Swaminathan Research Foundation |publisher=Mssrf.org |accessdate=10 September 2012 |year=2010 |ref={{sfnRef|MS Swaminathan Research Foundatation|2010}} |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120910064218/http://www.mssrf.org/ |arc